reviews.review_text:
can't go wrong with set 2 decent sound and a great second set. it's amazing that, after the playing reprise...they come back with several more songs. as a "touchhead"... ..i felt like they surely could have ended it there and it would have been the greatest second set i ever saw..but they whipped these things out easily back in those days. 

thanks for letting me listen !
